body.paragraph:
 ‘‘Chahi, bhikkhave, dhammehi samannāgato bhikkhu abhabbo anadhigataṃ vā kusalaṃ dhammaṃ adhigantuṃ, adhigataṃ vā kusalaṃ dhammaṃ phātiṃ kātuṃphātikattuṃphātikātuṃ 
Note { id=0, line='3', referenceLine='14', original='phātikattuṃ (sī.), phātikātuṃ (syā. kaṃ. pī.)', type='auto', previous=' Chahi, bhikkhave, dhammehi samannāgato bhikkhu abhabbo anadhigataṃ vā kusalaṃ dhammaṃ adhigantuṃ, adhigataṃ vā kusalaṃ dhammaṃ phātiṃ kātuṃ '
	Alternative{lang='vri', text='kātuṃ'}
	Alternative{lang='sī.', text='phātikattuṃ'}
	Alternative{lang='syā. kaṃ. pī.', text='phātikātuṃ'}}
. Katamehi chahi? Idha, bhikkhave, bhikkhu  na āyakusalo ca hoti, na apāyakusalo ca hoti, na upāyakusalo ca hoti, anadhigatānaṃ kusalānaṃ dhammānaṃ adhigamāya na chandaṃ janeti, adhigate kusale dhamme na ārakkhatisārakkhati 
Note { id=1, line='13', referenceLine='14', original='sārakkhati (sī. syā. kaṃ. pī)', type='auto', previous=' na āyakusalo ca hoti, na apāyakusalo ca hoti, na upāyakusalo ca hoti, anadhigatānaṃ kusalānaṃ dhammānaṃ adhigamāya na chandaṃ janeti, adhigate kusale dhamme na ārakkhati '
	Alternative{lang='vri', text='ārakkhati'}
	Alternative{lang='sī. syā. kaṃ. pī', text='sārakkhati'}}
, sātaccakiriyāya na sampādeti. Imehi kho, bhikkhave, chahi dhammehi samannāgato bhikkhu abhabbo anadhigataṃ vā kusalaṃ dhammaṃ adhigantuṃ, adhigataṃ vā kusalaṃ dhammaṃ phātiṃ kātuṃ.

 ‘‘Chahi, bhikkhave, dhammehi samannāgato bhikkhu nacirasseva mahantattaṃmahattaṃ 
Note { id=2, line='22', referenceLine='17', original='mahattaṃ (syā. kaṃ.)', type='auto', previous=' Chahi, bhikkhave, dhammehi samannāgato bhikkhu nacirasseva mahantattaṃ '
	Alternative{lang='vri', text='mahantattaṃ'}
	Alternative{lang='syā. kaṃ.', text='mahattaṃ'}}
pakaroti (ka.). Imehi kho, bhikkhave, chahi dhammehi samannāgato bhikkhu nacirasseva mahantattaṃ vepullattaṃ pāpuṇāti dhammesū’’ti. Chaṭṭhaṃ.

musāvādī hoti, pisuṇavācā hoti, pharusavāco hoti, samphappalāpī hoti, (sī. syā. pī.) evaṃ sukkapakkhepi? Pāṇātipātī hoti, adinnādāyī hoti, kāmesumicchācārī hoti, musāvādī hoti 
Note { id=5, line='47', referenceLine='22', original='musāvādī hoti, pisuṇavācā hoti, pharusavāco hoti, samphappalāpī hoti, (sī. syā. pī.) evaṃ sukkapakkhepi', type='auto', previous='? Pāṇātipātī hoti, adinnādāyī hoti, kāmesumicchācārī hoti, musāvādī hoti '
	Alternative{lang='vri', text='musāvādī hoti'}
	Alternative{lang='sī. syā. pī.', text='musāvādī hoti, pisuṇavācā hoti, pharusavāco hoti, samphappalāpī hoti,'}}
, luddho ca, pagabbho ca. Imehi kho, bhikkhave, chahi dhammehi samannāgato yathābhataṃ nikkhitto evaṃ niraye.

